  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Sauté the ginger and garlic until fragrant.",
    "Add cumin seeds and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the split red lentils and basmati rice, and stir to coat with ghee.",
    "Add 4 cups of water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15 minutes.",
    "Add lime leaves, turmeric powder, coriander powder, red chili powder, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Continue simmering, covered, for another 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in manteca and mix well.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional lime leaves if desired."
